                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18430703-2108-offence-1 t18430703-cd-31"></join>15th of June</rs>, at St. Luke, Chelsea, and stealing therein, 1 watch, value 2<hi rend="italic">l</hi>.; 1 snuff-box, 2<hi rend="italic">l</hi>.; part of a ring, 19<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; 1 pair of scissors, 1<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; 1 snap, 6<hi rend="italic">d</hi>.; his goods; and that he had been before convicted of felony.</rs>
